examples.en: Oil prices soared to a new record.
Up to the heavens, an eagle soared.
The value of his stocks has soared.
The rocket soared into the sky.
A hang glider soared in the air.
The nation's divorce rate has soared.
Her spirits soared at the sight of him.
The plane soared to heady heights.
Her voice, clear and pure, soared up to the roof.
The stock market soared after the cease-fire was announced.
